Some walls, called "earthwalls," are soft and can be battered down and destroyed. Run at the wall to your east until you pass through. Depending on your character's race and class, you may need to switch to a different attack skill such as `ready_skill punching or `ready_skill karate -- or wield a melee weapon if you have one.
endmsg
