msg
If your HP drops to zero, your character dies and respawns at the last Bed to Reality you used.  You will also lose experience points (which is permanent - but experience can be regained), and you also lose a random stat (Str, Dex, Con, etc. - which can be restored with a Potion of Life). Always set a Bed to Reality before entering dangerous areas, and retreat to heal rather than fighting to the death.
endmsg
